data.description: FANTASTIC Opportunity in Cross Creek!  LOCATION, LOCATION! Priced to Sell!  SOLD AS IS!!  This 2 bedroom 2 bath condo is ready for move in, or your renovations and updates. NO STEP entrance into condo from rear entry. Condo situated near gated entrance of community for easy in and out.   Located inside the perimeter, Cross Creek has it all!!!!  (2) Clubhouses available for resident rental  (3) pools  (4) tennis courts (2 with pickleball)   18-hole public, walking golf course  Cross Creek Café  The Gym at Cross Creek  Guest Suite available for rent for residents and their guests  Laundry facility located on Elysian for resident pay per use.  In town living in the heart of metro Atlanta!      .
